{"tid":2488154,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"耀才證券葉茂林轟美「唱衰香港」 移民潮、外資撤離令香港冇運行","createTime":"2021-04-14T05:01:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-14T05:36:30.000Z","uid":230530,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"8cbb48091157a399d601ddad74044d6b52930352","tid":2488154,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T05:01:30.000Z","msg":"港股近期較為波動，耀才證券集團主席葉茂林今出席活動時表示，港股隨新經濟股回調而下跌，但相信中概股回歸潮將推高日均交易至2,000、3,000億元，料今年恒指可望高見32,000點。<br />\n<br />\n他批評中美爭拗持續，美國帶頭「唱衰香港」，令人才移民、外資撤離，商舖又要待疫症緩和才有望回升，寫字樓更因企業撤資仍然受壓，他直言這樣下去「香港就冇運行。」他勸喻香港政府是時候「瞓醒」，建議馬上減利得稅及薪俸稅10%至12%，以重新吸引人才、外資及資金回流，「讓灰天鵝變成白天鵝。」"},{"pid":"80b0d4c19b00fe74dae8bba38aeba6c193f5c6cb","tid":2488154,"uid":18477,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T05:04:52.000Z","msg":"俗語有話<br />\n面係人哋俾<br />\n假係自己丟<br />\n<br />\nbtw唔係有萬能嘅国安髮就有運行啦咩洗乜驚畀人唱呀<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmSTErgTCbeoBsvjUeX58Dn3VrTzkkbxjsiW1GHogvMJ5C?filename=k9ZbGLG.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk9ZbGLG.gif&h=c609dc39&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ef4f9a538d496a3a5117fe6027f314b12dc1ec1d","tid":2488154,"uid":2054,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T05:07:38.000Z","msg":"金管局官方話無人走資<br />\n仲有資金流入<br />\n港共話好少人移民<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n夾好口供未呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65952c558198cc71677e379792fa13b5c9a75fb8","tid":2488154,"uid":25825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T05:08:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89dc54dfac0a6d8a8b1ad53127fc669728266e09","tid":2488154,"uid":25825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T05:09:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb2038adf1e6567e990df2ddbe050ac3203753fd","tid":2488154,"uid":25825